column2: ENGLISH
Hover over the event option for my levy efficiency law. If no tooltip appears, I have no dynlevy law applied.

Dynamic Levy Law: §Ydynlevy0_0§!
Levy Efficiency: §Y100%§!
Realm Size: §Y1§! through §Y19§!
Levy Efficiency
As your realm grows, your liege levy will grow with it. But by how much?
100% Realm Levy-Raising Efficiency

In a decentralized feudal system, rulers of large realms are less efficient at raising liege levies than rulers of smaller realms. Demesne levies are unaffected.

Smaller realms pack a harder punch per capita, all else being equal. For larger realms to compete per capita, they inevitably must centralize. See the EMF manual for details on levy efficiency.

Realm size class: §G1§! - §G19§!

Smaller realms pack a harder punch per capita, all else being equal. For larger realms to compete per capita, they inevitably must centralize. See the EMF manual for details on levy efficiency.
